OL,4,Ccontribute to drop in spring retail
OL,5,Csales figures
OL,7,FRetail sales dropped 4% in April
OL,8,Fversus the previous year, dampened by
OL,9,Fa spell of wet weather and an early
OL,10,FEaster bank holiday.
OL,12,FThe year-on-year drop is set against a
OL,13,Fgrowth of 5.1% in April 2023, but was
OL,14,Fartificially worsened by the earlier
OL,15,Ftiming of Easter, which previously
OL,16,Fpushed March sales unusually high,
OL,17,Faccording to the British Retail
OL,18,FConsortium (BRC)-KPMG Retail Sales
OL,19,FMonitor.
