OL,4,Ccontribute to drop in spring retail
OL,5,Csales figures
OL,7,FHelen Dickinson, chief executive of
OL,8,Fthe British Retail Consortium, said:
OL,9,F"Dismal weather and disappointing
OL,10,Fsales led to a depressing start to
OL,11,Fspring for retailers, even accounting
OL,12,Ffor the change in timing of Easter.
OL,14,F"Many retailers are hoping for
OL,15,Fbrighter sales over the summer months
OL,16,Fas social events ramp up, and consumer
OL,17,Fconfidence could improve with a
OL,18,Fpotential cut in interest rates."
