OL,7,FLinda Ellett, UK Head of Consumer,
OL,8,FRetail & Leisure, KPMG, said: "The
OL,9,Fpositive sales figures seen in March
OL,10,Fdue to an early Easter demonstrate the
OL,11,Fimportance that triggers such as
OL,12,Fwarmer weather, events and occasions
OL,13,Fcan have in helping to deliver the
OL,14,Fnecessary impact required to get
OL,15,Fconsumers spending again.
