OL,7,F"Retailers will be hoping that there
OL,8,Fmight still be an early summer
OL,9,Finterest rate cut, a strong
OL,10,Fperformance from England and Scotland
OL,11,Fin the Euros, and an uptick in
OL,12,Ftemperatures.
OL,14,F"Together this might be the trigger to
OL,15,Fboost consumers' willingness to spend
OL,16,Fin the weeks ahead."
